# Cursor Rules

This project uses AGENTS.md as the source of truth for all agent instructions.

@import AGENTS.md

## Cursor-Specific Notes

- Skills are located at `.agents/skills/` — read the relevant SKILL.md before starting a task
- Always follow the TDD mandate: write failing tests first
- Use data-testid selectors in E2E tests (never getByRole/getByLabel/getByText)
- Layer order: Domain → Database → API → Frontend → E2E
